"我知道你曾是一个冒险家", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "3238": {"data": {"tag_id": 3238, "tag_name": "GTA", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/tag/9a63c726856d98496e0e86df1d3096f5295f22f8.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "《侠盗猎车手》（Grand Theft Auto，简称 GTA，又译《横行霸道》、《侠盗猎车》、《侠盗飞车》、《侠盗车手》）是一系列以犯罪为主题的动作游戏，由 Rockstar North负责开发，Rockstar Games 发行。在游戏中，玩家扮演城市中的犯罪角色，透过完成一连串有组织罪案的任务来提升自己的威势，任务通常为枪战、抢银行、行刺等，其他犯罪以外的任务则有驾驶出租车、救火、赛车、飞行等。侠盗猎车手也因给玩家在游戏内随心所欲、自由度高而知名，它不像传统的动作游戏般只有单向式的历程，但在侠盗猎车手中，玩家可随意选择先玩的任务", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "572691": {"data": {"tag_id": 572691, "tag_name": "主机游戏", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 1}, "day_count": 1}, "263133": {"data": {"tag_id": 263133, "tag_name": "R星", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "74373": {"data": {"tag_id": 74373, "tag_name": "游戏杂谈", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/tag/6057e57134c1f2e7960cb7daa18aa350e6721dc0.png", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 1}, "day_count": 1}, "110374": {"data": {"tag_id": 110374, "tag_name": "游戏推荐", "cover": "",