友想必对“全明星”一词并不陌生吧。\n　　说道全明星，一般都会想到鬼畜，鬼畜原本是一个贬义词,源自日语，原意指像魔鬼畜生一样残酷无情。\n　　而在NICONICO和BiliBili出现的全明星鬼畜类型MAD则多指通过视频（或音频）剪辑，用频率极高的重复画面（或声音）组合而成的一段节奏配合音画同步率极高的一类视频。", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 1}, "day_count": 1}, "7782": {"data": {"tag_id": 7782, "tag_name": "三国演义", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/tag/75fd325ef255b04d4209c3b57c0722560643aac5.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "三国电视剧和电视剧衍生视频\r\n根据中国古典文学四大名著之一的《三国演义》改编电视剧和电视剧衍生，剧演述的是三国时代的故事，是魏、蜀、吴的兴亡史，起于桃园结义，终于三国归晋。着重表现的是从东汉末年到西晋初年将近一个世纪中多个政治集团间错综复杂、紧张尖锐的斗争，这种斗争发展成为连接不断的对政治权力的争夺和军事冲突，给人们描绘出三国时代政治风云的彩色画卷，展示出一幅幅波澜壮阔、惊心动魄的战斗风云图。\r\n", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "3221": {"data": {"tag_id": 3221, "tag_name": "娱乐", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "66": {"data": {"tag_id": 66, "tag_name": "洗脑", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "51330": {"data": {"tag_id": 51330, "tag_name": "诸葛亮", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/tag/1065b9c93da3cac5f4f5a0080bdb47176a646719.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "诸葛亮，字孔明、号卧龙。三国时期蜀汉丞相、杰出的政治家、军事家、散文家、书法家。著有《出师表》、《诫子书》等。曾发明木牛流马、孔明灯、诸葛连弩。中国古代忠臣的楷模，文学家常写文章以表达对其的赞赏。其鞠躬精粹，死而后已的形象为后世所铭记", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "68": {"data": {"tag_id": 68, "tag_name": "鬼畜", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/5f42290e9299eceb7dfce4b932b497d1255ea847.jpg", "head_cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/af941ccd50c12c1ccd91869bfcc6fb22d71b458f.png", "content": "起源于NICONICO动画，由最早出现的音MAD《最终鬼畜妹フランドール・S》中的“鬼畜”略称而得名。", "short_content": "以音频调教创作为主体的二次创作", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "39203": {"data": {"tag_id": 39203, "tag_name": "智斗", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 0, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "921692": {"data": {"tag_id": 921692, "tag_name": "对对子", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 0, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 1}, "day_count": 1}, "96659312": {"data": {"tag_id": 96659312, "tag_name": "BILIBILI17周年", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 0, "state": 0, "ctime": 1781783677, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "358": {"data": {"tag_id": 358, "tag_name": "动画", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "13015": {"data": {"tag_i